<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>sva</unclear>stiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> mal<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi>maṇṭalattuk kaṭur tāṉattu—
<lb n="2"/>—k koyil maṅkala<unclear>t</unclear> teva viṇṇa—<note n="192-1">The beginnings and the ends of the lines are built in.</note> 
<lb n="3"/>—ṉukku ca<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>ntr</unclear>ā</hi>ti<hi rend="grantha">tya</hi>vaṟ celvatāka Ik—
<lb n="4"/>—ṭippār va<hi rend="grantha">śa</hi>m poliūṭṭāka vai<hi rend="grantha">—</hi><note n="192-2">The rest of the record is lost.</note>
